ef="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sheffield-leadmill-lose-planning-application-to-gut-parts-of-the-venue-if-evicted-3838744">计划申请拆除场地某些部分的申请</a>后几天就进行的。该场地目前的租户米尔斯（Mills）此前曾表示，如果被迫撤离该建筑物，他打算将其目前的固定装置和配件的场所“肠道”（包括舞池和舞台）。</p><p>拒绝拟议拆除的计划官将其称为“无目的”，没有公共利益，并补充说，如果被驱逐出境，则应“将建筑物综合大楼归还到租赁之前的状态”。</p><p>在2022年出现了有关其受到威胁的消息后，前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jeremy-corbyn-joins-campaign-to-save-sheffield-leadmill-3227527">劳工领袖杰里米·科宾（Jeremy Corbyn）访问了领导者，并鼓励其他人“落后于此</a>。他还回应了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/leadmill-sheffield-eviction-closure-arctic-monkeys-tour-manager-local-reaction-3201505">无数的谢菲尔德当地人的景色</a>，称其为“城市的心脏”，以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/local-stars-rally-around-leadmill-as-new-owners-register-for-name-electric-sheffield-3197594">北极猴子，贾维斯·科克（Jarvis Cocker）所保持的立场，并将我的Sheffield艺术家中的Horiz Horie Oli Sykes带到了支持中。场地</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_2630524" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2630524" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-2630524" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_theleadmill_press_2000x1270.jpg" alt="谢菲尔德的领导台" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_theleadmill_press_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_theleadmill_press_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_theleadmill_press_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_theleadmill_press_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_theleadmill_press_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/2020_theleadmill_press_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2630524" class="wp-caption-text">谢菲尔德信贷中的Leadmill：Leadmill</figcaption></figure><p>多年来，谢菲尔德的理查德·霍利（Richard Hawley）也一直是<a href="https://www.nme.com/ne