i）和布雷克·莱弗利（Blake Lively）在2024年1月12日在新泽西州泽西城的“与我们结束”的集合中看到。 （摄于Jose Perez/Bauer-Griffin/GC图像）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Justin-Baldoni-and-Blake-Lively-on-set.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Justin-Baldoni-and-Blake-Lively-on-set-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Justin-Baldoni-and-Blake-Lively-on-set-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Justin-Baldoni-and-Blake-Lively-on-set-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Justin-Baldoni-and-Blake-Lively-on-set-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/Justin-Baldoni-and-Blake-Lively-on-set-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blake-lively">布雷克·莱弗利（Blake Lively）</a>声称，贾斯汀·巴尔多尼（Justin Baldoni）在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/it-ends-with-us"><em>这一组中使另外两个演员“不舒服”与我们结束</em></a><em>-</em>他们愿意在法庭上作证。</p><p>莱弗利（Lively） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/blake-lively-sues-it-ends-with-us-co-star-justin-baldoni-over-severe-emotional-distress-3824279">向加利福尼亚州民权部门针对巴尔多尼（Baldoni）提起了性骚扰和报复投诉</a>，指责他“不适当和不受欢迎的行为”，并声称他试图“摧毁”她的声誉。巴尔多尼（Baldoni）否认了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/justin-baldoni-sues-blake-lively-and-ryan-reynolds-claiming-they-tried-to-destroy-him-3829679">1月16日的所有指控和反击</a>，包括Lively的丈夫<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-reynolds">Ryan Reynolds</a>和公关人员Leslie Sloane。</p><p>在Lively的诉讼之后，Baldoni <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/it-ends-with-us-star-justin-baldoni-dropped-by-talent-agency-following-blake-lively-allegations-3824326">被他的人才代理机构William Morris Endeavor（WME）抛弃</a>。他还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/justin-baldonis-womens-solidarity-award-rescinded-over-blake-lively-allegations-3824731">取消了妇女团结奖。</a></p><p>在昨晚深夜（2月18日）提出的一项修订的投诉中，Lively声称她并不是唯一一个让Baldoni感到不舒服的人。</p><p> “多发性硬化症。 Lively并不孤单地抱怨Baldoni先生，并在2023年出现时同时提出了她的担忧。 “重要的是，与整个叙述被告发明的相反，巴尔多尼先生当时以书面形式承认了这些投诉。他知道，除了Lively女士以外的其他女性也不舒服，并且抱怨自己的行为。”</p><p>这些妇女没有命名，但投诉说，她们“允许Lively女士分享其通信的实质”，并“他们将在发现过程中作证并产生响应式文件”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3839588" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3839588" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3839588" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blake-lively-the-stewart-of-ny-1.jpg" alt="布雷克·莱弗利（Blake Lively）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blake-lively-the-stewart-of-ny-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blake-lively-the-stewart-of-ny-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blake-lively-the-stewart-of-ny-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blake-lively-the-stewart-of-ny-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blake-lively-the-stewart-of-ny-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/blake-lively-the-stewart-of-ny-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3839588" class="wp-caption-text">布雷克·莱弗利（Blake Lively）。图片来源：Stewart NY/Getty</figcaption></figure><p> Lively声称，在她在2023年5月报告自己的担忧之后，“另一位女性演员”也做了同样的事情。</p><p>投诉说：“尽管女性演员的大量保留，但她还是说话，但她还是表达了自己的感受，即由于巴尔多尼先生的举止，这部电影的作品正在遭受痛苦。” “多发性硬化症。吉亚内蒂（Gianetti）与Wayfarer分享了这些担忧。”</p><p> According to the complaint, Baldoni wrote to the female cast member in June, “acknowledging that he was aware of her concerns, and that adjustments would be made.”但是，该文件声称，Wayfarer“没有采取任何措施调查这一报告的行为，当时也没有实施任何保护。”</p><p> The suit goes on to allege that on June 8, the same female cast member shared with Lively her “growing concerns with the conditions on set.” Lively responded: “I know I find it really hard to speak to him. I try to cover it with busyness but not sure that covers what&#39;s going on.</p><p> “Later, another female cast member confided to Ms. Lively that she too felt uncomfortable on set. All of this occurred, and was documented in writing, almost one year before the editing of the Film began.” </p><figure id="attachment_3783332" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3783332" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3783332" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_blakelively_sonypictures_2000x1270.jpg" alt="Blake Lively and Justin Baldoni in 'It Ends With Us'" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_blakelively_sonypictures_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_blakelively_sonypictures_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_blakelively_sonypictures_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_blakelively_sonypictures_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_blakelively_sonypictures_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024_blakelively_sonypictures_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3783332" class="wp-caption-text"> Blake Lively and Justin Baldoni in &#39;It Ends With Us&#39; CREDIT: Sony Pictures Entertainment</figcaption></figure><p> In addition, a defamation claim has been added to the suit, Lively alleged that Baldoni&#39;s lawyer, Bryan Freedman, has issued “inflammatory content to media outlets” and has been “saying anything, whether true or false, that will harm Ms. Lively&#39;s credibility and intimidate others from speaking up on her behalf.” Crisis PR representative Jed Wallace, who has worked with Baldoni&#39;s team, is now named as a defendant in the suit along with his company, Street Relations Inc.</p><p> In a statement to <a href="https://variety.com/2025/film/news/blake-lively-justin-baldoni-made-two-other-women-uncomfortable-set-1236312765/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Variety</em></a> , Baldoni and Wayfarer&#39;s legal team said: “Our clients have been transparent in providing receipts, real time documents and video showing a completely different story than what has been manipulated and cherry picked to the media. Our clients have taken this matter and these issues very seriously notwithstanding the jokes made publicly by the plaintiff and her husband.</p><p> “Her underwhelming amended complaint is filled with unsubstantial hearsay of unnamed persons who are clearly no longer willing to come forward or publicly support her claims. Since documents do not lie and people do, the upcoming depositions of those who initially supported Ms. Lively&#39;s false claims and those who are witnesses to her own behavior will be enlightening. What is truly uncomfortable here is Ms. Lively&#39;s lack of actual evidence.”</p><p> In December, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/justin-baldoni-files-250million-suit-against-new-york-times-for-cherry-picked-blake-lively-story-3825472">Baldoni sued <em>The New York Times</em> ,</a> which reported Lively&#39;s allegations. In a statement to US outlet <a href="https://www.npr.org/2025/01/17/nx-s1-5262565/blake-lively-justin-baldoni-ryan-reynolds-it-ends-with-us-lawsuit#:~:text=Justin%20Baldoni%20has%20sued%20Blake%20Lively%2C%20Ryan%20Reynolds%20for%20%24400%20million&amp;text=Actor%20and%20director%20Justin%20Baldoni,for%20%24400%20million%20in%20damages." target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>NPR</em></a> , the newspaper said they “plan to vigorously defend against the lawsuit”.</p><p> Meanwhile, Baldoni, his company Wayfarer Studios and his current publicity team <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/justin-baldoni-sued-by-his-former-publicist-over-alleged-breach-of-contract-and-smear-campaign-3824746">are being sued by his former publicist</a> over alleged breach of contract and the purported smear campai